{"tid":534150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭虐打致死5歲小妹妹臨臨設靈","createTime":"2018-01-19T13:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T16:04:47.000Z","uid":39539,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"31fae7546359ef74e5baff16467ec559650e1bd8","tid":534150,"uid":39539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/214643_c5088fa6e6779526c9376e22d7ab82d2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F214643_c5088fa6e6779526c9376e22d7ab82d2.png&h=e2512886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下午5時許，臨臨多名親友抵達殯儀館佈置靈堂，葬禮採道教儀式進行，靈堂中央放置臨臨生前一張穿著紅色上衣，面帶微笑的照片，橫匾放置「永遠懷念」四個大字。<br />\n靈堂佈置簡約，放置多個淺黃色百合花的花籃，當中臨臨生母所送的花籃放於靈堂正中央，上放「陳瑞臨愛女安息，媽媽痛輓」紙牌，旁邊則有臨臨外公外婆及二叔等多名長輩親友送贈的花牌。<br />\n供桌上除放置鮮果，亦有零食，益力多等零食，以及多個卡通人物迷你兵團的公仔，至於臨臨生前就讀的屯門路德會富泰幼兒園亦有家長送來花牌致祭，入夜後親友陸續到來致祭，其間多名年長親友哀傷痛哭，需由其他親友擁抱安慰。"},{"pid":"4b7f427f44b1efb856578bd67b215dac61d7b736","tid":534150,"uid":115082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:50:47.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"406eb3ef66ac8e7f5067b0019ae2496f4958c5b6","tid":534150,"uid":53524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T15:04:38.000Z","msg":"2013－2018"},{"pid":"cfdae7cfbd4df68ba2ea027183eb20c424e6f7f1","tid":534150,"uid":6721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c22ae07fc2a1dd36abaedf49d9d3459b3f86b85","tid":534150,"uid":156659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T15:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b5266d531e33edfd94bef1d2063822c80c0b4d","tid":534150,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a34